      <div id="right_content">
        <div class="content_title">Undergraduate Programs</div>
        <div class="content_text">
          <div class="layout_2">
            <p align="left"><strong>Field of Study:</strong>&nbsp;<a href="http://isc.sjtu.edu.cn/undergraduate_programs.html" target="_blank"><strong><span style="color: #990000;">List of Undergraduate Programs</span></strong></a><br /><strong>Program Duration: 4 years&nbsp;</strong><br /><strong>Qualifications of Applicants:</strong></p>
<p align="left">1.	Healthy, non-Chinese citizen, foreign visa holders with senior high school diploma (or above). Applicants under 18 years old should submit Guardian's Guarantee Statement&nbsp;<a href="http://isc.sjtu.edu.cn/files/Guarantee%20Statement.pdf" target="_blank"><strong><span style="color: #990000;">(download online)</span></strong></a>;<br />2.	The applicants of mainland China, Hong Kong, Macau and Taiwan who have immigrated to other countries must hold foreign visa or nationality certificate for 4 years or above, and in the last 4 years (before May 15, 2015) must actually have lived abroad more than 2 years (more than 9 months of residence abroad per year may be considered as one year).</p>
<p align="left">&nbsp;</p>
<p align="left"><strong>Application Materials</strong></p>
<p align="left">1.	Senior high school diploma or equivalent (Graduating students should provide an official statement as proof of graduation<br />2.	Official transcripts (or equivalent) from your high school, including courses taken;<br />3.	If you apply for the undergraduate program of Chinese Language, a minimum requirement of HSK 4 (180 or above) is needed to prove your Chinese language proficiency;<br />4.	Applicants applying for exemption should provide relevant certificates (See "Exemption Requirements");<br />5.	One photocopy of your passport and two passport size photos;<br />6.	Application fee CNY 800 (approx.US$ 140)<br />7.	Applicants under 18 years old should provide "Guardian's Guarantee Statement".</p>
<p align="left">&nbsp;</p>
<p align="left"><strong>Application Procedure &amp; Application Period</strong></p>
<p align="left">Step 1: Apply online and upload the scanned application materials mentioned above.&nbsp;<a href="http://apply.sjtu.edu.cn/" target="_blank"><strong><span style="color: #990000;">(Apply online)</span></strong></a>.<br />Application website will be available in March, 2015. (Please visit&nbsp;<a href="http://global.sjtu.edu.cn/students/apply-to-sjtu" target="_blank">http://global.sjtu.edu.cn/students/apply-to-sjtu</a>&nbsp;or<a href="http://isc.sjtu.edu.cn/" target="_blank">http://isc.sjtu.edu.cn</a>&nbsp;to get the newest information.)<br /><br />Step 2: The original materials should be sent or submitted to the admission office (Room 1011, Tao Li Yuan building, 1954 Huashan Rd.)</p>
<table border="1" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0">
