<p align="left">Note: All materials should be sent to SJTU before deadline. Otherwise enrollment may be rejected.</p>
<p align="left">&nbsp;</p>
<p align="left"><strong>Entrance Test</strong><br />1.	Students applying for the majors listed as "Liberal Arts" or "Science" will have to attend the corresponding exams organized by SJTU (according to the first choice of major).<br />2.	Test Date &amp; Place</p>
