<p align="left"><span>4. SJTU 2015 International Students Entrance Examination Syllabus &amp; Sample Questions（</span><a href="http://isc.sjtu.edu.cn/files/2015-SJTU-test-sample.pdf"><strong><span style="color: #990000;">PDF</span></strong></a><strong>）</strong></p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p align="left"><strong>Notes:</strong><br />&diams;&nbsp; All the tests are close-book, and in Chinese;<br />&diams;&nbsp; Students applying for majors listed as "science" only need to choose two subjects from physics, Chemistry and Biology (for details about the test subjects, please see "2015 SJTU undergraduate programs list &amp; test subjects");&nbsp;<br />&diams;&nbsp; Students applying for the majors listed as both "science" and "liberal arts" can choose the test category by themselves.</p>
<p align="left"><strong><br /></strong></p>
<p align="left"><strong>Exemption Requirements</strong><br />1.	Students who wish to apply for exemption should qualify the following requirements :</p>
