<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p align="left"><strong>Admission Policies</strong><br />1.	Applicants who get sufficient scores will be accepted.<br />2.	Applicants who satisfy the exemption requirements will be accepted.<br />3.	Applicants who have various awards can get additional scores after the certification materials are approved by the university. Please take the award certifications with you at the time of registration.</p>
